f new strong lenses, the\nlens-redshift test could offer a powerful tool to probe cosmology as well as\ngalaxy evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 May 2007 19:40:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Aug 2007 19:27:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-06-23"}
