tios. We conclude that, in combination with other molecular gas\ntracers like CO, HCN, and HCO+, CN is an important probe of the physical\nconditions and chemical composition of dense molecular environments at high\nredshift.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 May 2007 11:18:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-06-23"}
